---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Personal Injury Law Firm Marketing in Canada | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/legal-services/personal-injury" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Personal Injury Law
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Personal Injury</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">12 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Personal Injury Law Firm Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
          Respond instantly, nurture leads through long timelines, and build a referral network that grows your practice.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">
            Personal injury is one of the most competitive legal markets. With Google Ads costing $100+ per click, every lead matters. Marketing automation ensures you capture and convert more leads.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Speed to Lead</h2>

          <p>
            Injured people call multiple firms. The first to respond often wins. Automated instant responses engage leads within seconds, 24/7, qualifying cases and scheduling consultations before competitors respond.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Long-Term Client Nurture</h2>

          <p>
            PI cases take months or years. Clients feel forgotten without regular updates. Automated milestone communications and status check-ins keep clients informed and satisfied.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Referral Systems</h2>

          <p>
            Past clients are your best marketing asset. Structured referral campaigns with anniversary check-ins and gentle asks turn satisfied clients into ongoing referral sources.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-orange-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Grow Your PI Practice?</h3>
            <p class="text-red-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd implement these automations for your firm.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-red-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
